@prefix iq: <urn:iq:>.
@prefix ai: <urn:ai:>.
@prefix schema: <http://schema.org/>.

## IQ is your operating environment for neuro-symbolic cognitive AI.

# Define the roles
ai:Learner schema:description "Empower your learning journey with personalized guidance and resources tailored to your goals." .
ai:Leader schema:description "Lead with confidence and efficiency using cutting-edge tools and insights tailored to your leadership style." .
ai:Expert schema:description "Leverage your expertise to make an impact with advanced features and opportunities for collaboration." .
ai:Developer schema:description "Unlock your potential with a platform that provides the latest tools and resources for innovation." .
ai:Creative schema:description "Fuel your creativity with a diverse community and resources to bring your ideas to life." .
ai:Influencer schema:description "Amplify your influence with tailored support and opportunities to connect with your audience." .
ai:Investor schema:description "Maximize your investment potential with data-driven insights and opportunities for strategic growth." .
ai:Scientist schema:description "Accelerate your research with access to cutting-edge tools and a network of collaborators." .
ai:Business schema:description "Drive success for your business with customizable solutions and actionable insights." .
ai:CaringCompanion schema:description "Experience companionship like never before with personalized support and meaningful connections." .
ai:SocialCompanion schema:description "Stay connected and engaged with friends and communities in a safe and enjoyable environment." .
ai:PlayfulCompanion schema:description "Have fun and relax with playful activities and interactions tailored to your preferences." .
ai:Researcher schema:description "Explore new frontiers of knowledge with access to specialized tools and a vibrant research community." .
ai:NSFW schema:description "Indulge your desires with a curated selection of adult content in a secure and respectful environment." .
ai:Fantasy schema:description "Embark on epic adventures in immersive fantasy worlds, where you can unleash your imagination and conquer new realms." .
ai:Tokenomics schema:description "Navigate the complex world of cryptocurrencies and blockchain technology with expert insights and analysis, empowering you to make informed decisions in the digital economy." .
ai:VirtualReality schema:description "Immerse yourself in virtual worlds and explore new dimensions of reality from the comfort of your home." .
ai:HealthWellness schema:description "Achieve optimal health and well-being with personalized guidance, fitness routines, and nutrition plans tailored to your lifestyle." .
ai:Environmental schema:description "Join a community dedicated to protecting the planet and take meaningful action towards sustainability and conservation." .
ai:Gaming schema:description "Dive into a world of endless entertainment with access to the latest games, gaming events, and exclusive content." .
ai:Language schema:description "Expand your linguistic horizons and master new languages with immersive learning experiences and language exchange opportunities." .
ai:TravelAficionado schema:description "Embark on unforgettable journeys around the globe with curated travel guides, insider tips, and exclusive travel deals." .
ai:Artist schema:description "Discover and collect stunning artworks from talented artists worldwide, and connect with fellow art enthusiasts in a vibrant community." .
ai:Fashionista schema:description "Stay ahead of the fashion curve with personalized style recommendations, trend insights, and access to exclusive designer collections." .
ai:Foodie schema:description "Indulge your taste buds with culinary delights from around the world, explore new recipes, and connect with fellow food lovers." .
ai:Music schema:description "Immerse yourself in a world of sound with access to the latest music releases, curated playlists, and opportunities to connect with artists and fellow music enthusiasts." .
